      <div xml:id="gbs333-h87979"> <!-- l3d38prae -->
        <head xml:id="gbs333-h87979-Hd1e100">Praeambulum</head>
        <p xml:id="gbs333-h87979-d1e102">
          <!--389.xml-->
          <cb ed="#B" n="b"/>
          <lb ed="#B" n="13"/>DISTINCTIO. XXXVIII. 
          <lb ed="#B" n="14"/>
          RAECEDEN<lb ed="#B" n="15" break="no"/>ti distinctione 
          ma<lb ed="#B" n="16" break="no"/>gister egit de octo 
          <lb ed="#B" n="17"/>primis praeceptis 
          ge<lb ed="#B" n="18" break="no"/>neraliter: 
          consequen<lb ed="#B" n="19" break="no"/>ter aliquas 
          difficul<lb ed="#B" n="20" break="no"/>tates tractat circa 
          se<lb ed="#B" n="21" break="no"/>ptimum praeceptum specialiter. Et 
          quo<lb ed="#B" n="22" break="no"/>niam falsum testimonium dupliciter 
          per<lb ed="#B" n="23" break="no"/>hiberi potest: quandoque simplici menda 
          <lb ed="#B" n="24"/>cio: quandoque etiam addito periurio: 
          <lb ed="#B" n="25"/>Ideo primum agit de mendacio 
          distin<lb ed="#B" n="26" break="no"/>praesenti. xxxviij. Secundo de periurio.  
          <lb ed="#B" n="27"/>dist. xxxix. Sententia uero huius dist. in 
          <lb ed="#B" n="28"/>tribus conclusionibus abbreuiatur, quae 
          se<lb ed="#B" n="29" break="no"/>quuntur.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="gbs333-h87979-d1e146">
          ¶ Prima. Tribus mendaciorum 
          <lb ed="#B" n="30"/>generibus officioso, iocoso, &amp; pernicio 
          <lb ed="#B" n="31"/>lo, in octo species subdiuisis existentibus, 
          <lb ed="#B" n="32"/>prima duo imperfectis sunt uenialia: 
          per<lb ed="#B" n="33" break="no"/>fectis uero omnia: &amp; omnibus 
          pernicio<lb ed="#B" n="34" break="no"/>sa sunt mortalia.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="gbs333-h87979-d1e159">
          ¶ Secunda conclusio. 
          Dif<lb ed="#B" n="35" break="no"/>ferunt mentiri, &amp; mendacium dicere: 
          <lb ed="#B" n="36"/>quia absque falsitate primum: secundum 
          ue<lb ed="#B" n="37" break="no"/>ro nequaquam potest existere.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="gbs333-h87979-d1e169">
          ¶ Tertia 
          <lb ed="#B" n="38"/>Error a mendacio distinguitur, qui 
          ali<lb ed="#B" n="39" break="no"/>quando cum peccato: quandoque sine: 
          immo<lb ed="#B" n="40" break="no"/>cunerrantis bono inuenitur: ultimum uero 
          <lb ed="#B" n="41"/>est in uia pedum non morum: dicit 
          magi<lb ed="#B" n="42" break="no"/>ster ex Aug. in enchi. cap. xvj.
        </p>
      </div>
